 Shortly after 7pm paramedics from ER24 arrived on the N1 north near Gordon Road where they found a male pedestrian with fatal injuries. He was still lying in the middle lane of the highway. There was nothing that paramedics could do for him and he was declared dead on the scene. An hour later paramedics from ER24 responded to another pedestrian that was knocked down on the N1 near Beyers Naude Drive. Paramedics found the man lying in the middle of the road with fatal injuries. He was later declared dead on the scene said ER24 spokesman Werner Vermaak.The vehicle that collided with the pedestrian was also hit by another vehicle after it came to a standstill on the highway he said. Three people including a child sustained minor injuries. They were all assessed and treated on the scene.